HEADLINE: SPANISH GOVERNMENT PREPARES NEW SET OF ELECTRICITY TARIFFS TO AVOID
"
CALIFORNIA EXPERIENCE" (EL GOBIERNO PRAPARA UN NUEVO MODELO DE TARIFAS
ELECTRICAS PARA EVITAR LA "EXPERIENCIA CALIFORNIA")

